      <% @products.each do |product| %>

        <div class="product_box">
          <h2><%= product.title %></h2>
        </div>

      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>






<div id="blurb" class="grid_12 border">

  <div class="centered">
    <p>
      The Letterspace project is a celebration of letterform in everyday spaces founded by designer and educator, Lucy Biggs. 26 designers are currently working to create the inaugural Letterspace alphabet spanning spaces across the UK, America, Canada, Europe and the Middle East. The alphabet will be launched at The Whitworth, Manchester, in April 2018.
    </p>

    <p>
      Each letter will be screen printed in a limited edition of 26 by print maker, Dan Mather, in London, with each designer selecting a bespoke ink and paper.
    </p>

    <p>
      A full set of the 26 letters will be auctioned at The Whitworth, with all proceeds donated to Mustard Tree and Printed by Us.
    </p>

    <p>
      The posters will also be available to buy at The Whitworth and online from April 2018.
    </p>

    <p>
      The Letterspace project is kindly and generously supported by Slater Harrison and Manchester School of Art.
    </p>

  </div>
</div>

